Whereas it would be nice if it included additional data, such as Project-key, Issue-key, as currently the only relation between the comment and the issue is given by the issueID provided in the {{self}} field in the webhook body.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Cloud*. Using *JIRA Server*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JRASERVER-31384].
  {panel}

The JQL query language lacks the possibility to return a limited number of issues from a search, compare with SQL LIMIT or TOP statements.

This would be very valuable when you want to get e.g. the 10 highest ranked stories.
